assignEmployer(EmployerRepository, Long, Employee) - Static method in class edu.sjsu.cmpe275.utils.EmployerUtils
Assigns Employer with employerId to an Employee.

If employerId is null, method returns with false because employerId is a mandatory field for an employee.
If there doesn't exist an employer with employerId, method return false indicating failure.

Note: this utility won't save employee into database, all changes are in-memory
assignManager(EmployeeRepository, Long, Employee) - Static method in class edu.sjsu.cmpe275.utils.EmployeeUtils
Assigns Manager with managerId to an employee.

If managerId is null, method returns true.
If Manager with managerId doesn't exist, method returns false indicating failure
If Manager's employer is not same as employee, method returns false indicating failure
otherwise, assigns the manager and returns true.

Note: this utility won't save employee into database, all changes are in-memory
